title: EBTOYS Clothesline Retractable and Adjustable Clothes Line Stainless Steel Clothes Dryer Laundry Indoor Outdoor
feature: This adjustable clothesline can extend to 2.8（9.7 feet）and hold a weight of approximately 5 kg（11 pound).

description: This retractable indoor clothes line is made of high quality 304 stainless steel and braided nylon line. It is suitable for hanging clothes or towels etc for bedroom, bathroom or hotel. With sturdy and durable design, the raided nylon line is strong to hold 5kg. And the stainless steel spring can reels up effortlessly. - Material: 304 Stainless Steel, Nylon. - Size: Approx. 9 * 9 * 2.8cm/ 3.54 * 3.54 * 1.1 inch.Diameter: 92mm. - This adjustable clothesline can extend to 2.8（9.7 feet）and hold a weight of approximately 5 kg（11 pound). - Stainless steel housing, durable fiber clothesline rop, automatically retracts. - Works great for hanging lightweight items that can't be done in dryer to dry. - Application to indoors or outdoors (laundry room, bathroom, balcony, even an RV or boat). - Comes with installation screws pack, easy to install. - Applications to household living room, kitchen, toilet, balcony, hotel, bathroom, even on a boat.
